
@font-face {
  font-family: "TradeGothic";
  src:url("../fonts/TradeGothic.eot"); /* IE9 Compat Modes */
  src:url("../fonts/TradeGothic.eot#iefix") format("embedded-opentype"), /* IE6-IE8 */
      url("../fonts/TradeGothic.otf") format("opentype"), /* Open Type Font */
      url("../images/TradeGothic.svg") format("svg"), /* Legacy iOS */
      url("../fonts/TradeGothic.ttf") format("truetype"), /* Safari, Android, iOS */
      url("../fonts/TradeGothic.woff") format("woff"), /* Modern Browsers */
      url("../fonts/TradeGothic.woff2") format("woff2"); /* Modern Browsers */
  font-weight: normal;
  font-style: normal;
}

@font-face {
    font-family: 'TradeGothic LT CondEighteen';
    src:url('../fonts/TradeGothicLT-CondEighteen.woff2') format('woff2'),
        url('../fonts/TradeGothicLT-CondEighteen.woff') format('woff'),
        url('../fonts/TradeGothicLT-CondEighteen.ttf') format('truetype'),
        url('../images/TradeGothicLT-CondEighteen.svg#TradeGothicLT-CondEighteen') format('svg');
    font-weight: 500;
    font-style: normal;
}

  font-family: "TradeGothic-BoldCondTwenty";

      url("../fonts/TradeGothicBoldCondensedNo20.otf") format("opentype"), 
      url("../images/TradeGothicBoldCondensedNo20.svg") format("svg"), 
      url("../fonts/TradeGothicBoldCondensedNo20.ttf") format("truetype"), 
      url("../fonts/TradeGothicBoldCondensedNo20.woff") format("woff"), 
      url("../fonts/TradeGothicBoldCondensedNo20.woff2") format("woff2"); 
  font-weight: normal;
  font-style: normal;
}
